dct_title_s: Mapa geologico de Honduras. Santa Maria del Real, hoja 3060 III G
dct_description_sm: Honduras. Instituto Geografico Nacional. Tennessee Technological University. Honduras. Direccion General de Minas e Hidrocarburos. North Decimal Degree 14.833300. South Decimal Degree 14.6667. East Decimal Degree -85.7500. West Decimal Degree -86.0000. Alternate title: Mapa geologico Santa Maria del Real, Honduras, C. A. In upper margin: Geologia Honduras 1:50,000. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 m. contour interval and spot heights. Verso: "Perfil geologico sin exageracion vertical.".
